data.description: This gorgeous 3 level, 5 bedroom 4.5 bath home features a grandiose floor plan with gleaming hardwood floors on the main level.  The kitchen offers a breakfast bar and an island with stainless steel appliances and loads of counter space. A cook's dream kitchen with double ovens, 42" cabinets and a walk-in pantry. The living room has 2 story ceilings with floor to ceiling windows. The dining room has ornate ceiling details with arches that open up to the living room for easy entertaining. There are two oversized Master suites to choose from one on the main and the other on the 2nd level both with seating areas and closet space galore. There is a loft space overlooking the living room on the second level and a movie room and bonus room on the 3rd level! There is also a 3 car garage and screened in porch overlooking the manicured backyard. So many more things to list about this home you must just see it for yourself.
